creased during this time period,\nbut the geometry and black hole mass remain unchanged, which confirms that the\nBLR kinematics suitably gauge the gravitational field of the central black\nhole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Oct 2020 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-21"}
