 a cart-pole toy\nproblem and a quadrotor avoiding obstacles, and show that clustering samples\nbased on inherent structure improves the warm-start quality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2020 14:24:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 13:24:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Mar 2021 14:18:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-25"}
